ENTRY            F0695   20251222   20260311   20260311       F107
SUBENT        F0695001   20251222   20260311   20260311       F107
BIB                 10         22
TITLE      Prevalence of the 8Be formation in the
           7Li(d,alpha alpha n) reaction at Ed = 7.0 MeV
AUTHOR     (N.Arena,Seb.Cavallaro,R.Potenza,V.D.Amigo,G.Fazio,
           S.Femino,G.Giardina,S.Jannelli,M.Lombardi)
INSTITUTE  (2ITYCAT,2ITYLNS,2ITYSIC,2ITYMES,2ITYPAD)
REFERENCE  (J,NCL,23,1,1978)
FACILITY   (VDG,2ITYPAD) 7.5 MV
DETECTOR   (SIBAR) Two ORTEC surface barrier detectors were used.
           One of these reminded in a fixed position at polar
           angle of 82 degrees and azimuth angle of 0 degree and
           also acted as a beam monitor. The other detector was
           allowed to rotate between 50 and 90 degrees at azimuth
           angle of 180 degrees.
METHOD     (BCINT,COINC)
SAMPLE     (3-LI-7,ENR=0.999) A 7LiF target 0.5 mg/cm2 thick.
           The target (placed at 45 degrees with respect to the
           beam) was obtained by vacuum evaporation of 7LiF,
           enriched to 99.9% in 7Li, onto a carbon backing of
           40 ug/cm2.
ERR-ANALYS (DATA-ERR) No information about source of uncertainty
HISTORY    (20010514C)
           (20251222A) SD: Small corrections in all Subents.
ENDBIB              22
COMMON               1          3
EN
MEV
 7.
ENDCOMMON            3
ENDSUBENT           29
SUBENT        F0695002   20251222   20260311   20260311       F107
BIB                  6         14
REACTION   (3-LI-7(D,N+A)2-HE-4,,DA/DA/DE,A/A/A+A,REL)
            No information about units.
ANG-SEC    (ANG1,A)
           ANG1 is a polar angle of the first alpha-particle
            detected.
           (ANG2,A)
           ANG2 is a polar angle of the second alpha-particle
            detected.
EN-SEC     (S,A) the kinematic locus of the energies of the
           2 alpha particles.
ERR-ANALYS (E-ERR-DIG) Digitizing error in the kinematic locus of
            the energies of the 2 alpha particles.
STATUS     (CURVE,,N.Arena+,J,NCL,23,1,1978) Fig.1
HISTORY    (20251222A) SD: BIB updated. DATA-ERR1 -> E-ERR-DIG.
ENDBIB              14
COMMON               3          3
ANG1       E-ERR-DIG  ERR-DIG
ADEG       MEV        ARB-UNITS
       -82.       0.02      0.001
ENDCOMMON            3
